{
  "doc_id": "53236",
  "text": "Cryo-preserved ovarian tissue can be used in healthy women who wish to preserve fertility for non-medical reasons. With vitrification methods the cryo-preserved ovarian tissue is similar to fresh ovarian tissue regarding viability and integrity [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Transplantation of the cryo-preserved ovarian tissue restores hormonal function and fertility [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
